README for github.com/crithead/xercerc/
=======================================

This is an example projects showing how to parse XML files with Xerces-C++
version 3.1.1.

https://xerces.apache.org

Programming Guide:
http://xerces.apache.org/xerces-c/program-3.html

Installation
------------

1. Install Xerces-C++ development libraries (Debian)

.............................................................................
# aptitude install libxerces-c-dev libxerces-c-doc libxerces-c-samples
.............................................................................

2. Build & Run

.............................................................................
$ make
$ ./parser dictionary.xml
.............................................................................

